The issue was that when you visit `/shared/01204ece-07c3-41bf-8c5b-c1c09f3e546c`, the trip-planner.js was only looking for a `?trip=` query parameter, which didn't exist in the shared URL format. This caused it to redirect to dashboard, creating an infinite loop.

